# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manages an HAProxy backend (server pool) on OPNsense. Backends define groups of servers that HAProxy distributes traffic to, along with load balancing algorithm, health checks, and session persistence settings. Requires the `os-haproxy` plugin.

